DOC.brief_summary: The purpose study evaluate tear film stability DAILIES® AquaComfort Plus® ( DACP ) compare MyDay® 12 hour lens wear .
DOC.brief_title: Tear Film Stability DAILIES® AquaComfort Plus® Contact Lenses vs. MyDay® Daily Disposable Contact Lenses
